title: No. 23 Virginia Tech takes on No. 3 Louisville Sunday afternoon - VT hokiesports.com
content: No. 23 Virginia Tech takes on No. 3 Louisville Sunday afternoon  VT hokiesports.com
description: The Virginia Tech women's basketball team (20-6, 12-3) returns to the court on Sunday afternoon when they take on the third-ranked Louisville Cardinals (22-3, 13-2).
